ploads/2025/05/absolvement-ferium-race.png?w=1200\" alt=\"Ferium race from the Absolvement Roblox experience\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e25% Fire Resistance\u003c/mark\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e7 Mana\u003c/mark\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e–\u003c/strong\u003e25% Frost Resistance\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e–\u003c/strong\u003e10% Holy Resistance\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e Increased base Mana pool\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e High resistance to \u003cmark\u003eFire\u003c/mark\u003e damage\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e−\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e Reduced resistances make fighting certain enemies a lot harder\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd data-align=\"center\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/absolvement-harmonite-race.png?w=1200\" alt=\"Harmonite race from the Absolvement Roblox experience\"/\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cmark\u003eNo buffs, and no debuffs\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e No debuffs\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cmark\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e−\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e\u003c/mark\u003e No buffs\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eCharacter images via the \u003ca href=\"https://trello.com/b/KgOCR48n/absolvement-community-trello\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\"\u003eAbsolvement Community Trello\u003c/a\u003e Wiki board.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"h-how-to-change-races-in-absolvement\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eHow to Change Races in Absolvement\u003c/h2\u003e    \u003cfigure data-wp-context=\"{\u0026#34;imageId\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;68520c58abc2d\u0026#34;}\" data-wp-interactive=\"core/image\" data-current-count=\"300\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" data-wp-class--hide=\"state.isContentHidden\" data-wp-class--show=\"state.isContentVisible\" data-wp-init=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async--click=\"actions.showLightbox\" data-wp-on-async--load=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" data-wp-on-async-window--resize=\"callbacks.setButtonStyles\" src=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/how-to-change-race-in-absolvement.png?resize=1200%2C675\" alt=\"Preview of the Character creation menu in Absolvement Roblox experience where one can change their race.\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eYou can change your race when creating a new Character.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e    \u003cp data-characters=\"212\" data-current-count=\"512\" data-injectable=\"true\"\u003eIn Absolvement, \u003cstrong\u003eyou can change your race only when creating your character\u003c/strong\u003e. Choosing a race is free, but it is also permanent. So, it is good practice to consider all race options before starting a new character.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp data-characters=\"196\" data-current-count=\"196\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThat concludes our Absolvement race tier list. Now, you are ready to delve into the black and white world as prepared as you can be. Also, check out our \u003ca href=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/definitive-absolvement-sin-tier-list/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eSins tier list\u003c/a\u003e for more Absolvement guides.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e    \u003chr data-injectable=\"false\"/\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"h-absolvement-race-tier-list-faqs\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003eAbsolvement Race Tier List FAQs\u003c/h2\u003e    \u003cdiv data-current-count=\"196\" data-injectable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"faq-question-1746533919043\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are the overall best Absolvement races?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eCurrently, the best races that are useful for most builds in Absolvement are \u003cstrong\u003eCragg\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eKatiyr\u003c/strong\u003e, and Kix’xm.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"faq-question-1746535492078\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCan you change your race after you finish creating a character?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnfortunately, \u003cstrong\u003eyou can’t change your race once you’ve created your character\u003c/strong\u003e in Absolvement. To choose a new race, you would have to make another character.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"faq-question-1746535672406\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are the best races for beginners in Absolvement?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe best races for beginners are \u003cstrong\u003eGelidium\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eKatiyr\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eKix’xm\u003c/strong\u003e because they work well with most builds and because they are suitable for kiting enemies.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ci data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003e The Escapist is supported by our audience. When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn a small affiliate commission. \u003c/i\u003e\u003ci data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.escapistmagazine.com/affiliate-policy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-stringify-link=\"https://escapistmagazine.com/affiliate-policy\" data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\"\u003eLearn more about our Affiliate Policy\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\t\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
